name: Drone Lands Evacuation Plans
description:
A data pad containing a set of exhaustingly detailed and exactingly precise evacuation plans which reference the relocation of a large alliance based somewhere in the eastern side of New Eden. 

The data pad was discovered in the Lost & Found bin at the InterBus terminal of the Perkone Factory station in Uemon, the owner apparently forgetting to take it with them when they departed on their trip to Perrigen Falls.
